brainly_data.question: The astronomy club plans to wash cars to raise money for a new telescope. With tax, the telescope costs $327.19. Estimate how many cars will have to be washed to cover the entire cost of the telescope if the club charges $5.00 per car.
brainly_data.subject: Health

all_answers.question: The astronomy club plans to wash cars to raise money for a new telescope. With tax, the telescope costs $327.19. Estimate how many cars will have to be washed to cover the entire cost of the telescope if the club charges $5.00 per car.
all_answers.subject: Health
all_answers.text: Easy math here, $327.19/5.00=$65.43800. we can round that that to  65.44 dollars so in total they will need to wash at least 66 cars.
